acpi: acpi (command-line ACPI client)
acpi:
acpi: Attempts to replicate the functionality of the 'old' apm command
acpi: on ACPI systems, including battery and thermal information.
acpi: Does not support ACPI suspending, only displays information
acpi: about ACPI devices. 
acpi: 
acpi: http://sourceforge.net/projects/acpiclient/
acpi: 

